{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1977,"month":9,"day":9}],"page_start":6,"page_end":6,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"毛主席啊，战士看到您","authors":["王晓廉"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"三千里东风三千里雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"边疆战士怀念毛主席。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京城呵金色的城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日夜都在战士心头系。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"边疆战士到北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一心要看望毛主席。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，四十四根巨柱擎天宇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席纪念堂巍峨立。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼望金灿灿琉璃瓦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"步步登上玉阶梯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莹莹的水晶棺一色碧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慈祥的面容多刚毅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盼您想您呵——毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望穿云海度朝夕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年离别日月短呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛度过一世纪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席啊，战士此刻看到您，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟岸的身影多熟悉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说您和我们永别离？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分明是巡视过祖国刚休息。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您记挂着祖国山和水啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您走遍江河与大地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，走遍祖国今归来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脸庞安详无倦意。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚步放轻，再放轻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万万莫把领袖来惊起。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多想上前问声好啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汇报粉碎“四人帮”的新胜利！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华主席办事您放心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊天动地创奇迹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，抓纲治国向前进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，您的旗帜高高举。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金色的“五卷”四海飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光照长天和大地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席啊毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一切，您看了该有多欢喜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您欢喜呀战士心里甜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万丈海涛逐浪激。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此还北国守边疆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥刀跃马迎风雨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京、边疆山水遥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纪念堂永在心中立。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的导师毛主席啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远和我们在一起！"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}